title: Hour 1 - Jon Gruden May Be Attempting a Comeback
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Jon Gruden May Be Attempting a Comeback
description:
Dan reacts to an eventful cut down day in the NFL, highlighted by the Raiders releasing former first-round pick Alex Leatherwood. Dan discusses Jon Gruden publicly addressing his firing and explains why Gruden may already be plotting his return to football.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
